% Provides the official Ghent University style elements.
%
% The available colours are:
% - Main colours: ugent-blue and ugent-yellow
% - Faculty colours: ugent-{lettercode}, where lettrecode is the two-letter code
%
% The available fonts are:
% - /panofamily -> general fontspec font
% - /pano[size]{text}
% - /panosemibold[size]{text}
